moji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做人要識得感恩，珍惜當下。<br />\n<br />\n人生最緊要嘅係快樂，要喺有生之年做自己喜歡嘅事，能夠隨心所欲而且平衡生活先係真正嘅人生。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加句<br />\n我地永遠都唔會知下一秒發生嘅事，所以想做就去做，寧願做咗嚟後悔，都唔好冇做先後悔。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446c2c90cb94f68fa31d5a31ea1392146d8502a2","tid":182400,"uid":6648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"成功係留畀努力嘅人"},{"pid":"f6310c9d4f0614a1defb0d7047a973d61a7d0b06","tid":182400,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"機會係留畀有機會嘅人"},{"pid":"57ad72e6ad1f50315d31c3c4a314d873a47d31e2","tid":182400,"uid":7071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機會係留畀有機會嘅人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F7Jw638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF7Jw638.jpg&h=bffbbda9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ef94de4f6f6eef04b9e4771b037b64a723e90ee","tid":182400,"uid":92348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇錯就點都唔會道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做人要識得感恩，珍惜當下。<br />\n<br />\n人生最緊要嘅係快樂，要喺有生之年做自己喜歡嘅事，能夠隨心所欲而且平衡生活先係真正嘅人生。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加句<br />\n我地永遠都唔會知下一秒發生嘅事，所以想做就去做，寧願做咗嚟後悔，都唔好冇做先後悔。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有 只需要做好自己本分 人地要點係人地既事 問心無愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8da2d6278f93f44d3999b41c647dfbdbc6570c","tid":182400,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"來說是非者，便是是非人"},{"pid":"f161e88200107359edbfac7b2020658f34503066","tid":182400,"uid":23991,"like":0,"di